  <h1>Welcome to the Immersive Labs Cyber Dictionary Quiz</h1>
  <p>Answer the questions to learn all the terms you will need to survive in the cyber industry.</p>
  <%- if logged_in? %>
    <%= link_to 'Click here to start quizzing!', random_quizzes_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %><br><br>
